## Getting Started

Install dependencies:

```bash
bun install
```

Start in development mode (hot reload):

```bash
bun run dev
```

## Available Scripts

| Script | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `bun run dev` | Start with hot reload |
| `bun run start` | Start without hot reload |
| `bun run build` | Compile to `dist/` |
| `bun run test` | Run tests |
| `bun run lint` | Lint source files |
| `bun run format` | Format with Prettier |

## Scaffolding

Use the NemesisJS CLI to generate new components:

```bash
nemesis generate controller users
nemesis generate service users
nemesis generate module auth
nemesis generate resource posts   # full CRUD module
```

